description:
Tarot Card & Art Noveau

If you want to donate towards costs and don't want to subscribe:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

VAE needed because it fixes my facial nightmares.
Use the 56000 VAE that's pruned with your Stable Diffusion installation.

Also noted: Our clip skip is at 2. We didn't use hi res fix, but did upscale with R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B on a couple of the pics.

Safetensors format to come.

Trained on VERY small amounts of Anime, Tarot Card & Art Noveau.
